Subject: RE: [VB] open deck lid for better cooling?

I don't see where we are in disagreement.  The top of the decklid is the
best place for air intake on a bug, which is why the vents are there.  The
bottom of the decklid isn't the place to pull air in due to the proximity
of the warm air leaving the engine.

